first step: take pizza base  
second step: put pizza sauce on the pizza
third step: put grated cheese on the pizza
fourth step: put toppings on the pizza like: baby corn, tomato, capsicum
fifth step: put the pizza in oven at 170 degrees and heat for 20mins
sixth step: now pizza is ready to eat 
seventh step: now put little grated cheese
last step: cut the pizza in to 8 pieces